{"tid":1793722,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚食冬至飯，見到隔離枱反枱","createTime":"2019-12-22T15:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:08:50.000Z","uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"26cb70b328315229543de4f6004182fc6944a121","tid":1793722,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:01:34.000Z","msg":"今晚同屋企人食冬至飯，等左成20分鐘終於可以食條魚，諗住舞下龍頭，有頭有尾。<br />\n<br />\n丫，你老味，夾緊個龍頭既時候，隔離枱個毒撚夠膽死砰一聲反枱，我俾佢嚇到成個龍頭跌撚左落地。大佬，我等成廿分鐘就係要食個龍頭，而家係 無 . 撚 . 左 . 呀<br />\n<br />\n當我諗住拎住魚頭問條死毒撚做咩撚野反枱既時候，有條弱智經理追出黎問我食唔食生果。屌丫，嬲到我將個魚頭一野車落條經理個口黎，咁鐘意食食龍吐珠啦。<br />\n<br />\n好地地一餐冬至飯都咁樣，條毒撚咪俾我再見到你。"},{"pid":"b1323125240511d39da21e87c67a08921aa57e39","tid":1793722,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:03:45.000Z","msg":"【正式宣佈】 12.25 SUCK the Christmas 聖誕三部曲行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793712</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"97fd1f3eca8efb220f0b386fc12cdffac3761bb8","tid":1793722,"uid":167674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:04:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人食冬至飯食撚到反尻埋張枱！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793444</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n相認？"},{"pid":"8691d0971383aa708a77d1f89fbe00f21ebb7638","tid":1793722,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:05:53.000Z","msg":"嬲到我"},{"pid":"893ffb383fa62a57dfc2814ab9773532781241a0","tid":1793722,"uid":210088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCT5Wcz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCT5Wcz.gif&h=0737b662&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}